        <legality>3</legality>
        <weight>2800</weight>
        <cost>3000</cost>

        <short>4mm gauss rifle.</short>
        <description>
            <para>
                Semi-automatic gauss rifle, the standard weapon of the
                Imperial Army, and available to civilians as well. It is
                not fully automatic, but is capable of selective fire.
                Some governments only allow modified versions which have
                the selective fire capability removed.
            </para>
        </description>
